    "description": "We at Meritnation Ventures Solutions are looking for an experienced Subject Matter Expert based out of Srinagar. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Meritnation Ventures Solutions:\nMeritnation Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n• Proficiency in Zoom/Teams\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Meritnation Ventures Solutions!",
